<i>♪ We're not gonna take it </i>

1072
00:55:04.437 --> 00:55:06.674
<i>♪ No. we ain't gonna take it </i>

1073
00:55:07.675 --> 00:55:11.646
<i>♪ We're not gonna</i>
<i>take it anymore ♪</i>

1074
00:55:13.648 --> 00:55:16.449
<i>♪ We're not gonna take it </i>

1075
00:55:17.018 --> 00:55:19.687
<i>♪ No. we ain't gonna take it </i>

1076
00:55:20.521 --> 00:55:25.560
<i>♪ We're not gonna</i>
<i>take it anymore ♪</i>

1077
